{"abstract":[{"text":"Some components can be used for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"actions","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/actions"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"level":3,"text":"Buttons","anchor":"Buttons","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_button_enabled_strong_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout with text only, icon only or text and icon."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Four hierarchies are proposed for all layouts: "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"strong"}]},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"minimal"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"negative"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Two style are available: "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"loading","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If button is placed on colored surface using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSColoredSurface"},{"type":"text","text":", the default colors (content, background and border) are automatically adjusted to switch to monochrom."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A button with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSButton.Hierarchy.Negative"},{"type":"text","text":" hierarchy is not allowed as a direct or indirect child of an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSColoredSurface"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["     \/\/ Icon only with default hierarchy","     OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), hierarchy: .default) {}","","     \/\/ Text only with negative hierarchy","     OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", hierarchy: .negative) {}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For accessibility reasons, if the user in the system settings toggles the option to reduce the animations, the loading indicator will be frozen to be more comfortable for the user.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For ecodesign reasons, if the user toggles the low power mode, the loading indicator will be frozen to prevent the CPU to work and waste energy."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"article","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Actions","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"Actions","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"images":[{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"card"}]},"sections":[],"references":{"component_button_enabled_strong_Orange":{"identifier":"component_button_enabled_strong_Orange","type":"image","alt":"A button component in light and dark mode with Orange theme","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_button_enabled_strong_Orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"title":"Components","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components pr